Yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin kasashen EU/EEA da kuma United Kingdom wanda ya tabbatar da cewa annobar COVID-19 tana tashi cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe, yayin da take da matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa.
Dangane da gogewa daga Italiya, ya kamata ƙasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don saurin karuwar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawar lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton rukunin cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtuka da ba a sani ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020 ne Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta China ta sanar da cewa cutar ta Coronavirus, wadda yanzu ake kira da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 ta zama mai haddasa cutar.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa an sake masa suna Coronavirus Disease (COVID-19).
Shaidar da ke akwai a yau ita ce, kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da cutar mai laushi, wato cututtukan numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar nimoniya ba kuma yawancin waɗannan suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya zama mafi munin cuta wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari na shari'o'in suna da mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Halin mutuwar da aka yi wa marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su a asibiti sakamakon COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin ɗari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin yanayin cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin EU / EEA da United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK da Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris, 2020.
COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da samun ci gaba ta hanyar yanayin ƙasa kuma a halin yanzu, cutar ta COVID-19 ta kasance mafi girma a duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
An ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'in COVID-19 na Turai da aka tabbatar da farko bisa ga ma'anar shari'ar WHO a cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris, 2020 na Eurosurveillance, Spiteri et al.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon kamuwa da cutar guda uku da aka tabbatar a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
Har zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK), tare da 39,768 da mutuwar 1,771 da aka ruwaito tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan ranar, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kawai.
